      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know. i've talked to people. it doesn't matter. nothing changes. it just feels like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. there's no \"path forward\" when everything that made life worth living is just... gone. it's just an empty house now. i don't want to \"navigate\" anything. i just want the hurting to stop. permanently.",
