    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so loud. the silence in this house is so loud. i look at the bed and it's just... it's so much. like i'm just supposed to keep breathing and eating and sleeping every single day like nothing happened? like the last decade didn't just get erased? it feels like a joke. a cruel, exhausting joke. i'm just so tired of fighting to stay in a world that doesn't even have them in it anymore.",
